Tags: you would receive [] if the only relevant tags were "1" and "7"

and they were both made of the same word: "brunch" and "food".

Examples:

[input] => {"description":"sausage
    \nbreakfast"
        "tags" : [

        1 ][xxxxxxxx]

    ] ==(output)==

    []   "5"

    //The event has relevant tags "sausage"

//    "food" and "brunch" which were made
    //of the same word
